nodes.text: This unidentified star was a giant blue-white star located in the Centrality, a sector of the Outer Rim Territories. It was the primary star of the Dilonexa system.
The name of this star was a catalogue number.

This giant blue-white star was orbited by forty planets. The nearest twenty-two planets were too hot, while the outer seventeen planets were too cold. The planet in the middle, Dilonexa XXIII, was the only one that could support life.
Dilonexa XXIII was a rich agriworld that served as the breadbasket of the Centrality.
